OL,3,COpening date confirmed for final
OL,4,CNorthumberland Line station
OL,6,FNorthumberland County Council has
OL,7,Fannounced the opening date for the
OL,8,Ffinal station on the Northumberland
OL,9,FLine.
OL,11,FBedlington, the sixth station to be
OL,12,Fcompleted since the line opened in
OL,13,FDecember 2024, will open to passengers
OL,14,Fon Sunday 29 March.
OL,16,FOver a million passenger journeys have
OL,17,Fbeen made on the line in the 14 months
OL,18,Fsince services began running between
OL,19,FNewcastle and Ashington.
