OL,3,COpening date confirmed for final
OL,4,CNorthumberland Line station
OL,6,FAshington and Seaton Delaval were the
OL,7,Ffirst stations to open, followed by
OL,8,FNewsham in March 2025, and Blyth
OL,9,FBebside in October 2025.
OL,11,FNorthumberland Park is set to open on
OL,12,FSaturday 22 February 2026, with
OL,13,FBedlington completing the set the
OL,14,Ffollowing month.
OL,16,FThe first trains to stop at Bedlington
OL,17,Fon Sunday 29 March will be the 8.28am
OL,18,Ftowards Ashington, followed by the
OL,19,F8.43am towards Newcastle.
