OL,4,CNorthumberland Line station
OL,6,FNorthumberland County Council Leader
OL,7,FGlen Sanderson said: "I am absolutely
OL,8,Fdelighted to be able to confirm
OL,9,FBedlington opening for March 2026.
OL,11,F"It's the culmination of so much work,
OL,12,Fled by the County Council, but it
OL,13,Fwouldn't have been possible without
OL,14,Feveryone else who has been so integral
OL,15,Fto making the Northumberland Line the
OL,16,Fsuccess it is.
