OL,6,F"I also want to thank the local
OL,7,Fcommunity ` I know they've been
OL,8,Flooking forward to a station in
OL,9,FBedlington for a long time and they've
OL,10,Fbeen watching it go up, as well as
OL,11,Ffacing some inevitable disruption that
OL,12,Fgoes with major infrastructure works,
OL,14,F"But we've made it and are so much
OL,15,Flooking forward to welcoming
OL,16,Fpassengers next month."
