OL,3,COpening date confirmed for final
OL,4,CNorthumberland Line station
OL,6,FAlex Hornby, Northern's Commercial and
OL,7,FCustomer Director, said: "We're
OL,8,Flooking forward to the opening of the
OL,9,Ffinal station on the Northumberland
OL,10,FLine so we can welcome customers on
OL,11,Fboard in Bedlington.
OL,13,F"Transforming an old freight line into
OL,14,Fa busy passenger railway with six new
OL,15,Fstations hasn't been easy, but all of
OL,16,Fthat hard work is paying off as it's
OL,17,Fhaving a huge impact on the region.
OL,18,FThis is the all-important final piece
OL,19,Fof the puzzle and another landmark
OL,20,Fmoment for us all.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUuD@AOU
