OL,6,F"Well over one million journeys have
OL,7,Fbeen made on the line so far, with
OL,8,Fcustomers making the most of our
OL,9,Fquick, reliable and affordable
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,F"Opening Northumberland Park later
OL,13,Fthis month and Bedlington in March
OL,14,Fwill allow even more people to
OL,15,Fbenefit, whether they're travelling
OL,16,Finto work or heading out to see
OL,17,Ffriends and family."
